Feature: Product Search Functionality

  Scenario Outline: Enter  search term and verify  results
    Given I open the browser and enter the URL 
     
   When I enter  product name as '<validproductName>' in the search bar
    And I click on the search button
    Then relevant results should be displayed
    When I enter product name as '<empty>' in the search bar
    And I click on the search button
     Then no results should be displayed
     When I enter product name as '<invalidproductName>' in the search bar
     And I click on the search button
     Then no results should be displayed for an invalid product name
     When I enter product name as '<mispelledproductName>' in the search bar
     And I click on the search button
     Then the system should suggest a correction for the misspelled product name
    When I enter  product name as '<validproductName2>' in the search bar
    And I click on the search button
     Then relevant results should be displayed
     Examples:
   
| validproductName|      |empty|      |invalidproductName|  |mispelledproductName|   |validproductName2                     |                   
                                   
| sofa            |      |     |       |   perfumes      |  |  chopa                 |Industrial Tan 90cm Studded Back Bench|                    
                                   
                                     
    
